(5, 'Stephen Chbosky', 'I don’t know if you’ve ever felt like that. That you wanted to sleep for a thousand years. Or just not exist. Or just not be aware that you do exist. Or something like that', 'The Perks of Being a Wallflower', 'Healthy sleep', 'https://www.goodreads.com/quotes/tag/sleep', '3_5.jpg', NULL, NULL),
