(7, 'Laini Taylor', 'Hope can be a powerful force. Maybe there\'s no actual magic in it, but when you know what you hope for most and hold it like a light within you, you can make things happen, almost like magic', 'Daughter of Smoke & Bone', 'Hopelessness', 'https://www.goodreads.com/quotes/tag/hopelessness', '3_7.jpg', NULL, NULL),
